      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/797/565/original/aed9add0-e45d-4d30-b58f-a7843eb6d4b3.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="275" width="158">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7b4fd5a0-87bc-468d-a2f6-6b53b02a5a0b" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_details" data-step-uuid="8045a9bf-b826-47ab-8efd-d85217bb0fd2">
    <h2 id="open_course_details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Course Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/176/139/original/838f73e1-12b3-4572-9166-ec879236ee07.png" srcset="" alt="Open Course Details" height="82" width="670">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_fae34045-6332-4487-af13-3d6359581c57" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Course Details</strong> tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_restriction_options" data-step-uuid="CE5218B9-2701-4F96-BB44-5CFDE6A72F02">
    <h2 id="view_restriction_options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Quantitative Data Options</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/797/567/original/952cef4b-d1df-4860-b5d7-4e3be308b9c8.png" srcset="" alt="View Quantitative Data Options" height="56" width="502">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DDF3C26A-FE8C-449B-8989-98A12AC846E4" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Course Details tab, locate the Quantitative Data Options. To restrict students and observers from viewing quantitative data, click the <strong>Restrict view of quantitative data</strong> checkbox.</p>
<p>By default, the Restrict view of quantitative data checkbox is not selected, meaning students and parents/observers can view numeric data as well as letter grades and comments. To retain this default for the course, do not select the checkbox. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> If the checkbox is selected and grayed out, your admin has locked the account-level setting.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="update_course_details" data-step-uuid="fbaf308a-67d3-4344-8f69-288a76df8b60">
    <h2 id="update_course_details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Update Course Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/797/569/original/f750db99-505e-48ab-ac34-1c6c1a358cd3.png" srcset="" alt="Update Course Details" height="65" width="211">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_5893425e-79f8-4963-a616-7c56422122ee" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Update Course Details</strong> button. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
